image_analysis.description: A narrow, galley-style kitchen or pantry area. The room features off-white or cream-colored cabinetry that extends to the ceiling. A white top-freezer refrigerator is centered in the background. To the left, there is a small metal rolling cart. On the right, a stainless steel microwave sits on a light-colored countertop next to a sink. A wine rack is built into the cabinetry above the refrigerator. The floor is covered in a dark blue carpet. A circular flush-mount light fixture is on the ceiling.
